@* Razor host views live under Features/{Feature}/Views/ (e.g. FloorPlan.cshtml,
   PassiveMember Admin.cshtml). They embed Blazor components via the <component>
   tag helper, which must be registered here — the Views/_ViewImports.cshtml only
   applies to the Views/ tree, not to feature-local views. Without this, <component>
   is emitted as literal markup and nothing renders. *@
@addTagHelper *, Microsoft.AspNetCore.Mvc.TagHelpers
@addTagHelper *, Microsoft.AspNetCore.Mvc.Razor
